  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV24">
        <l>pirivakai yuṇarttalum pāṅki kūṟa</l>
<l>vuritaṉi ṉaḻuṅkalu maḻuṅkāk kālai</l>
<l>yaṟikuva ṉeṉṟalu maṟiyak kūṟalu</l>
<l>naṟunuta liṉaitalu nayavarak kūṟalun</l>
<l>teriyiḻai nērtaluñ celavuṭaṉ mayaṅkalum</l>
<l>vantatu poḻuteṉa varuntalun tōḻi</l>
<l>nontaṉa ḷuraippavu nōvāḷ kūṟṟu</l>
<l>māṟṟu vittalu māyiṭai varuvōṉ</l>
<l>mēṉavuñ cēyiṭaip piriveṉak koḷalē</l></lg>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV24comm1">eṉpatu cēy iṭaip pirivām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:id="TNV24comm2">pirivuṇarttutaṉ mutal ākap peyarntōṉ kūṟṟīṟākac collap paṭṭaṉa 
      cēy iṭaip pirivām eṉṟa vāṟu.</p>
      <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
<lg xml:id="TNV24poem1"> 
    <l>aṟaṉu mīkaiyu maṉpuṅ kiḷaiyum</l>
    <l>pukaḻum pōkamun tarutaliṟ puṟampeyarntu</l>
    <l>taruvatu tuṇintaṉam peritē</l>
    <l>viripūṅ kōtai viḷaṅkiḻai poruḷē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu1">eṉpatu talaimakaḷ tōḻikkup pirivuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
<lg xml:id="TNV24poem2"> 
    <l>evaṉpala moḻikō yāṉē yaṉpa</l>
    <l>vakaṉṟivaṭ pirinta vannilai</l>
    <l>nikaḻntaṉ ṟamma nīṅkuta luyirē</l>
</lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu2">eṉpatu tōḻi talaimakaṇilaimai kūṟic celavaḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem3"> 
        <l>yāṉoṉṟu kūṟuva ṉaiya vāṉa</l>
        <l>nilampaka vaṟanta pulampuṟu cēṇiṭaic</l>
        <l>ceyviṉai nayantaṉi rāyi ṉavviṉaik</l>
        <l>kammā varivaiyu māṟṟumō naṭaiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu3">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem4"> 
        <l>āṟucel varuttañ cīṟaṭi civappavuñ</l>
        <l>ciṉai nīṅku taḷiriṉ vaṇṇam vāṭavun</l>
        <l>tāṉvara ṟuṇinta vivaḷiṉu mivaḷoṭu</l>
        <l>vēypayi laḻuva muvakkumeṉ</l>
        <l>pētai neñcam peruntakai yuṭaittē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu4">eṉpatu talaimakaṉeñciṟkuc collic celavaḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem5" corresp="#KT71"> 
        <l>marunteṉiṉ maruntē vaippeṉiṉ vaippē</l>
        <l>yarumpiya cuṇaṅki ṉampakaṭ ṭiḷamulaip</l>
        <l>peruntō ṇuṇukiya nucuppiṟ</l>
        <l>kalkeḻu kāṉavar nalkuṟu makaḷē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu5">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem6"> 
        <l>kuṟittatai yituveṉa neṟippaṭak kūṟi</l>
        <l>yavaṇilai yaṟintiyāṉ moḻintapiṉ vaḻāatu</l>
        <l>poṉpuṉai neṭuntēr pūṇkaniṉ māvē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu6">eṉpatu aḻuṅkātu celavu kuṟitta talaimakaṉukkut tōḻi colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem7"> 
        <l>aṟiyēṉ ṟōḻiyavar neñcukuṟit tatuvē</l>
        <l>maṟipuṇar māṉpiṇai kalaiyoṭu maruvap</l>
        <l>parivuṟu mukatta rāki</l>
        <l>yorumuṟai yaṉṟi nōkkiṉar peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu7">eṉpatu tōḻi talaimakaṭkuk kuṟippiṉāṟ pirivuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem8"> 
        <l>varampil kēḷvip perumpeyarp paṉuval</l>
        <l>patiṉeṇ moḻiyiṟ payaṉkoḷa virikku</l>
        <l>matipurai kēḷvi matiyōr nacaiip</l>
        <l>pirivarnaṅ kātalar piṟapulam paṭarntē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu8">eṉpatu kalvi viḷakkuvāṉ pirivar eṉa veḷip paṭa vuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem9"> 
        <l>māyiru ñālat tuyirtalai yaḷikkuṅ</l>
        <l>kāval vēṇṭiṉar kātala</l>
        <l>rāyiḻai maṭantai yāṟṟutal kaṭaṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu9">eṉpatu kāttaṟkup pirivar eṉa vuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem10"> 
        <l>mīḷā veṉṟi yiruperu vēntarai</l>
        <l>vāḷama raḻuvam peyarkku</l>
        <l>māḷviṉaik kakalvarnam maṉpi ṉōrē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu10">eṉpatu pakai taṇippāṉ pirivar eṉa vuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem11"> 
        <l>velperun tāṉai vēntaṉ pakaimicaic</l>
        <l>celkuvar mātō kātala</l>
        <l>ralliyaṅ kōtai yaḻuṅkalō voḻiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu11">eṉpatu vēntaṟ kuṟṟuḻip pirivar eṉa vuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem12"> 
        <l>nāḷu nāḷu māḷviṉai yaḻuṅka</l>
        <l>villiruntu makiḻvōrk killaiyāṟ pukaḻeṉa</l>
        <l>voṇporuṭ kakalvarnaṅ kātalar</l>
        <l>kaṇpaṉi tuyaroḻi tōḻi nīyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu12">eṉpatu poruḷ vayiṟ pirivar eṉa vuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem13"> 
        <l>cēṟala reṉpa tuḷateṉi ṉuraimati</l>
        <l>māṟiṉar valvara luraippi</l>
        <l>ṉūṟiṉ ṟivvaḻi vāḻvōrk kuraiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu13">eṉpatu pirivar eṉpatu kēṭṭa talaimakaḷ āṟṟāḷyt tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem14" corresp="#KT22"> 
        <l>nīrvār kaṇṇai nīyiva ṇoḻiya</l>
        <l>yārē pirikiṟ pavarēc cāraṟ</l>
        <l>cilampaṇi koṇṭa valañcuri marāattu</l>
        <l>vēṉi lañciṉai kamaḻun</l>
        <l>tēmū coṇṇuta ṉiṉṉoṭuñ celavē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu14">eṉpatu āṟṟāḷ āya talaimakaṭkut tōḻi pirivu nayappac colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem15"> 
        <l>nallicai niṟuttal vēṇṭit tuṇaipirintu</l>
        <l>celvatu kātalar kaṭaṉē ceṉṟeṉa</l>
        <l>vōṅkiya vuḷḷamoṭu pulavā</l>
        <l>tillirun tāṟṟutal kaṟpiṉa tiyalpē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu15">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem16" corresp="#KT315"> 
        <l>eḻutaru matiyaṅ kaṭaṟkaṇ ṭāaṅ</l>
        <l>koḻukuveḷ ḷaruvi yōṅkumalai nāṭaṉ</l>
        <l>ñāyiṟ ṟaṉaiyaṉ ṟōḻi</l>
        <l>neruñci yaṉaiyaveṉ perumpaṇait tōḷē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu16">eṉpatu talaimakaḷ pirivuṭaṉ paṭṭatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem17"> 
        <l>aruñcurak kavalaiyum pirinteṉa varūum</l>
        <l>peruntaṇ vāṭaiyu niṉaii</l>
        <l>varuntuka memmai maṟavā tīmē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu17">eṉpatu pirivuṭaṉ paṭṭa talaimakaṭalaimakaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem18"> 
        <l>kāliya ṉeṭuntērk kaṭumpari kaṭaiip</l>
        <l>pālaik kāṉam pōki viṉaimuṭit</l>
        <l>tiṉṉē varuka nāmē</l>
        <l>poṉṉēr mēṉi pulamputavap peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu18">eṉpatu pirintu cellun talaimakaṉ ṟērp pākaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem19"> 
        <l>āṇṭava ṇoḻintaṉṟu milaiyē yīṇṭiva</l>
        <l>ṇeḻuviṉi vāḻiya ṉeñcē paṇimoḻi</l>
        <l>maiyē ruṇkaṇ kaluḻac</l>
        <l>ceyvatu tuṇinta poruḷvayi ṉāṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu19">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ iṭaic curattut talaimakaḷai niṉaintu neñciṉait teḷittuc ceṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem20"> 
        <l>cellā ravareṉa yāṉikan tēṉē</l>
        <l>yollā ḷivaḷeṉa voḻintaṉar</l>
        <l>nalleḻi luṇka ṇaliyumeṉ ṉeñcē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu20">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ aṟiyāmaṟ pirinta viṭattut talaimakaḷ āṟṟātu colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem21"> 
        <l>piṭavuṅ kōṭalum viraii maṭava</l>
        <l>tārīṉ koṉṟaiyoṭu tōṉṟi tōṉṟak</l>
        <l>kārkoṇ ṭaṉṟē kāṉa</l>
        <l>nīrkoṇ ṭaṉavāṟ ṟōḻiyem kaṇṇē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu21">eṉpatu paruvavaravu kaṇṭāṟṟāḷ āyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem22"> 
        <l>amma vāḻi tōḻi yavarpō</l>
        <l>ṉammuṭai vāḻkkai maṟantaṉṟu kollō</l>
        <l>maṉaiyeṟi yulakkaiyiṟ ṟiṉaikkiḷi kaṭiyuṅ</l>
        <l>kāṉa nāṭaṉ pirinteṉat</l>
        <l>tāṉum pirintaṉṟeṉ māmaik kaviṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu22">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem23"> 
        <l>ciṟupuṉ mālai ciṟupuṉ mālai</l>
        <l>tīppaṉip paṉṉa taṇvaḷi yacaiic</l>
        <l>cekkark koṇṭa ciṟupuṉ mālai</l>
        <l>vaikalum varutiyā lemakkē</l>
        <l>yeṉṟuñcel lāyavar kuṉṟukeḻu nāṭṭē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu23">eṉpatu talaimakaḷ āṟṟāmaikkut tōḻi yāṟṟāḷ āyiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem24"> 
        <l>niraiyir cellu mōveṉa nērntu</l>
        <l>pulaiya ṉeṟinta pūcaṟ ṟaṇṇumai</l>
        <l>ēva liḷaiyar tāyvayiṟu karikku</l>
        <l>miṉṉā varuñcura meṉpa</l>
        <l>teṉṉō tōḻiyavar ceṉṟa vāṟē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu24">eṉpatu āṟṟāḷ āya tōḻikkāṟṟuval eṉpatu paṭac colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem25"> 
        <l>kavvaiyam perumpaḻi tūṟṟa nalaṉiḻantu</l>
        <l>paitalañ ciṟunutal pacalai pāya</l>
        <l>nammitaṟ paṭutta vavariṉu mavarnāṭṭuk</l>
        <l>kuṉṟaṅ koṭiyako ṟōḻi</l>
        <l>yoṉṟun tōṉṟā maḻaimaṟan taṉavē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu25">tōḻi yāṟṟuvippāṉ ṟalaimakaṉai iyaṟ paḻittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem26"> 
        <l>toṭinaṭan tiḻiyac cāay tōḷavar</l>
        <l>koṭumai kūṟiṉa vāyiṉuṅ koṭumai</l>
        <l>nalvarai nāṭark killai tōḻiye</l>
        <l>ṉeñciṟ pirintatu milarētaṅ</l>
        <l>kuṉṟa nōkkaṅ kaṭintatu milarē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu26">eṉpatu talaimakaḷ ataṉukku āṟṟāḷ āy moḻintatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem27"> 
        <l>niṟainīr māmaḻai poṟaimelin turutteṉa</l>
        <l>vampat taṇpeya luṇarāḷ kaṇṭē</l>
        <l>kāreṉa varuntu mivaḷiṉu mivaḷvāyt</l>
        <l>tirunakai yeyiṟṟi ṉiṇarmukai yarumpiya</l>
        <l>peruntaṇ mullaiyu muṭaiyavā ṉakaiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu27">eṉpatu paruvam aṉṟeṉa vāṟṟuvittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem28"> 
        <l>kārē ceyta kāṉaṅ kaṉaipeyaṟ</l>
        <l>kōpa mūrnta koṅkucēr neṭuneṟi</l>
        <l>yuḷḷiṉu muḷḷa muvappap</l>
        <l>puḷḷeḻa vantaṉṟu neṭuntakai tērē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu28">eṉpatu tēr varavu kūṟi yāṟṟuvittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem29"> 
        <l>illamoṭu miṭainta kollai mullai</l>
        <l>pallāṉ kōvalar paiyu ḷāmpaṉ</l>
        <l>mayaṅkiruṇ mālai kēṭṭoṟuṅ</l>
        <l>kalaṅkuṅko laḷiyaṇaṅ kāta lōḷē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu29">eṉpatu viṉai muṭittu mīḷvāṉeñciṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem30"> 
        <l>vārā rāyiṉar kāta lōreṉa</l>
        <l>nīrvār kaṇṇiṉaḷ pulampak</l>
        <l>kārār māmukil kaṭuñcela voḻiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu30">eṉpatu mukilukkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem31"> 
        <l>ūrka pāka tērē kārkaṇṭu</l>
        <l>pācaṟai nīṭiṉar kāta lōreṉa</l>
        <l>nappulan tuṟaivōḷ kāṇa</l>
        <l>vippoḻu taḷavai pukuka nāmē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu31">eṉpatu tērppākaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem32"> 
        <l>kātalar varavu kāṭṭiṉai yākaliṟ</l>
        <l>cūḻkatirc curimukap matiyam</l>
        <l>vāḻiya malartalai yulakuḻai neṭitē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu32">eṉpatu tōḻi caṅkiṉai vāḻttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem33"> 
    <l>purikuḻaṉ maṭantai polivoṭu maṉpar</l>
    <l>varaviṉuk ketirntanam maka<space quantity="5" unit="character"/> viṉviḻa</l>
    <l>tu<space quantity="2" unit="character"/><space quantity="2" unit="character"/>ya payaṉē</l>
    </lg>
    <!--p xml:lang="en">I have decided here to present this poem in its fullest form as found in a manuscript - UVSL48032. It is not clear how UVC arrived at this text, as the palm-leaf MS has lost most of this poem. Perhaps it was more intact when he had access to it. Without any further information, I err on the side of inclusion.</p-->
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu33">eṉpatu talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV24poem34"> 
        <l>pirita lāṟṟumō niṉṉē yariti</l>
        <l>ṉuṭampāṇ ṭoḻintamai yallatu</l>
        <l>maṭaṅkeḻu nōkka marīiya neñcē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV24koḷu34">eṉpatu talaimakaṭkut talaimakaṉ colliyatu.<note> 24.</note></p>
</div>

